videos.headline: Coastal Carolina capitalizes on UMass passing mistake
videos.description: UMass QB Andrew Ford forces a late throw behind the line, leading to a fumble recovery for CCU.

videos.headline: Coastal Carolina is first on the board with a QB keeper
videos.description: Backup QB Dalton Demos finds a hole up the middle for a 1 yard rushing TD.

videos.headline: UMASS with a quick answer to tie the score at 7
videos.description: UMASS RB Marquis Young swings it around the outside and knots the game at 7.

videos.headline: Coastal Carolina Marcus Outlow shows off his great hands
videos.description: RB Marcus Outlow makes a diving catch look easy to move the chains for Coastal Carolina.

videos.headline: Coastal Carolina with a huge 4th down conversion
videos.description: RB Marcus Outlow pushes the pile and converts on 4th down to keep Coastal Carolina's drive alive.

videos.headline: QB Dalton Demos extends Coastal Carolina's lead with a great rushing TD
videos.description: Backup QB Dalton Demos runs it in from 22 yards for his second rushing TD of the night.

videos.headline: UMASS converts on 4th and moves the chain downfield
videos.description: QB Andrew Ford finds WR Brennon Dingle for a big 4th down conversion.

videos.headline: The Minutemen get the call on the TD pass to tie it up
videos.description: After the review, QB Andrew Ford connects with WR Andy Isabella for an iffy TD in the back corner to tie the score.

videos.headline: FUMBLE! Coastal Carolina with the strip and recovery
videos.description: UMass QB Ross Comis tries to run it up the gut, but Coastal Carolina's C.J. Brewer is there for the strip.

videos.headline: Coastal Carolina's Abercrombie churns it out for 17 yards
videos.description: RB Oshamar Abercrombie just keeps on going to put Coastal Carolina inside the 10 yard line.

videos.headline: Abercrombie uses his strength to regain the lead
videos.description: Back to back plays RB Oshamar Abercrombie gets the call. This time pushing it in from 4 yards away to give CCU the lead.

videos.headline: UMass caps a great drive with a QB keeper TD
videos.description: QB Andrew Ford scrambles and finds a lane to tie it up at 21

videos.headline: CCU RB Alex James has some agility to pick up 25 yards
videos.description: RB Alex James goes up the left side making defenders miss while picking up 25.

videos.headline: RB Marcus Outlow cuts it back to pick up 26 for CCU
videos.description: A great run from RB Outlow gives CCU great field position midway through the 3rd quarter.

videos.headline: Another 4th down conversion for UMASS sets up great field position
videos.description: Andy Isabella makes some moves and picks up a big first down to keep the ball moving for UMASS.

videos.headline: CCU VS UMASS
Abercrombie adds to incredible night and the Chanticleer's lead
videos.description: RB Osharmar Abercrombie scores again and further separates the Chanticleers from the Minutemen.

videos.headline: UMASS moving the ball quickly downfield with a 40-yard completion
videos.description: QB Andrew Ford connects with Andy Isabella for 40 yards as they try to move quickly.

videos.headline: UMASS answers on a 1-yard TD dash
videos.description: RB Marquis Young finds the endzone for the second time shrinking the CCU lead to 10.

videos.headline: CCU VS UMASS
